* Samuel Francis QAT disqualified for an anti-doping rule violation according to IOC Disciplinary Commissions desicion of August 30 2016. 




Men's 100 m - Athletics - Beijing 2008 Summer Olympics
Event Format:
     
     The 100 m race was run in straight lanes on the homestretch in the Stadium. Athletes competed in preliminary heats, quarterfinals, semifinals and final. The best athletes from each heat (Q) and a number of "lucky losers" (q) advanced to the next level. Event facts: Men's 100 m competition was held at the Beijing National Stadium and 80 athletes participated in the event.
